  "MaterialExpressionCustom": {
    "title": "Custom (自定义HLSL代码)",
    "description": "自定义HLSL代码节点，可编写任意着色器逻辑",
    "outputs": [{"name": "", "type": "depends on OutputType"}],
    "inputs": [{"name": "动态，通过 InputName[N] 设置", "type": "any"}],
    "settable_properties": {
      "Code": {"type": "string", "description": "HLSL 代码", "example": "return float3(1,0,0);"},
      "Description": {"type": "string", "description": "节点显示标题", "example": "PulseGlow"},
      "OutputType": {
        "type": "enum",
        "description": "输出类型",
        "values": ["CMOT_Float1", "CMOT_Float2", "CMOT_Float3", "CMOT_Float4", "CMOT_MaterialAttributes"]
      },
      "InputName[N]": {
        "type": "string",
        "description": "第N个输入的名称，N从0开始。HLSL代码中必须用此名称引用输入值",
        "example": "Time"
      }
    },
    "important_notes": [
      "⚠️ HLSL代码中的变量名必须和InputName完全一致，否则报 'undeclared identifier'",
      "⚠️ 操作顺序很重要：1.创建节点 → 2.连接输入 → 3.设InputName[0] → 4.设Code → 5.设OutputType → 6.重编译",
      "必须先连接输入节点（如Time），这样Inputs数组才会被填充，然后才能设置InputName",
      "如果不设置InputName，默认名称是'None'，HLSL编译会失败"
    ],
    "tags": ["custom", "hlsl", "code", "shader", "material"]
  },
  "MaterialExpressionLinearInterpolate": {
    "title": "LinearInterpolate / Lerp (线性插值)",
    "description": "在 A 和 B 之间按 Alpha 线性插值：result = A * (1-Alpha) + B * Alpha",
    "outputs": [{"name": "", "type": "same as inputs"}],
    "inputs": [
      {"name": "A", "type": "any"},
      {"name": "B", "type": "any"},
      {"name": "Alpha", "type": "float"}
    ],
    "settable_properties": {},
    "tags": ["lerp", "interpolate", "blend", "mix", "material"]
  },
